[30;1m3136 | [0m[35m  BFGS optimization to find linear weights for the blender that minimize mean absolute error[0m
[30;1m3137 | [0m[35m  (compared to the GLM blender, which finds linear weights that minimize RMSE), and the MAEL1[0m

[30;1m2103 | [0m[35m********[0m
